magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.stream

类 GathererSpliterator<T,A,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.stream.GathererSpliterator<T,A,R>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of input elements for the new gatherer.
    A - The type of the state of the returned initializer.
    R - The type of results for the new gatherer.
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.util.Spliterator<R>

    public class GathererSpliterator<T,A,R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Spliterator<R>
    An addition spliterator for Gatherer to provide functions which the source stream unsupported with Gatherer API contents. This is a pseudo spliterator to provide a start point of stream with unsupported source contents.

    This is a part of the port contents of Java 24 feature "Gatherer API" and we implement it with a spliterator and make it be the spliterator in pipeline of StreamSupport.

    作者:
    Magic_Sweepy
